@node "FEATURES" "What can it do?"

In Inept mode there is, except the usual Tetris blocks, a special block.
If you complete a row with one or more special blocks in something good, or bad, is gonna happen.

@{u}Special events:@{uu}

@{b}Jukebox:@{ub}     Use the up arrow to pick a tune. There are 3 different tunes;
             Rock 'n' roll, Slow rock and Metal.

@{b}Scorebandit:@{ub} If you look at the score display, you'll see a lever, just
             like the ones on slot machines.

PLUS that there are a bunch of things that doesn't need an explanation.

@endnode

@node "HOWTO" "How to play this nice game."

Ineptris is like Tetris. Everybody knows how to play Tetris...don't they?


@{u}In game keys:@{uu}

@{b}Up:@{ub}      Rotate block
@{b}Left:@{ub}    Move block left
@{b}Right:@{ub}   Move block right (wow)
@{b}Down:@{ub}    Increase speed down.

@{b}P:@{ub}       Toggle pause on/off.
@{b}Esc:@{ub}     Quit to main menu.


@{u}Menu controls:@{uu}

@{b}Up/Down:@{ub} Select item
@{b}Enter:@{ub}   Activate item     

@endnode

